---
title: Seared Fillet Steak & Roasted Veggies with Zesty Mixed Salad & Plant-Based Pesto Butter Sauce
description: Steak night always feels a bit luxurious, especially when prepared with a premium eye fillet steak and a flavourful plant-based pesto sauce drizzled over. Gather around the table with friends and family, raise your steak knives high, and let the feast begin!

